---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { METRICS } from '../config/metrics';
import { SITE } from '../config/site';
---

<Base title="About & how we test" description="Who is behind RoamTested and exactly how every eSIM gets scored.">
  <section class="wrap prose">
    <h1 class="page-title">About {SITE.name}</h1>

    <!-- 占位:你的笔名、一句话身份、为什么做这个站。想好了再填。 -->
    <p class="muted"><em>(<p>RoamTested is run by a trilingual traveler, testing every eSIM on the ground so you don't have to.</p>.)</em></p>

    <h2>How we test</h2>
    <p>
      Every eSIM reviewed here is bought with our own money and tested inside mainland China —
      not from a desk. Each provider goes through the same protocol and is scored 0–10 on
      {METRICS.length} weighted criteria:
    </p>

    <ul>
      {METRICS.map((m) => (
        <li>
          <strong>{m.label}</strong> ({m.weight}%) — {m.blurb}
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>

    <p>
      Speed figures are medians of three Ookla Speedtest runs at the same spot, VPN off,
      background downloads paused. App access is checked app by app on cellular data only.
      Every data table carries the city and date it was tested, and results are re-tested on
      each return trip.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions, corrections, or an eSIM you want tested:
      <a href={`mailto:${SITE.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.contactEmail}</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-title { padding-top: 2rem; }
</style>
